name: Hamunaptra Style 2.1
description:
This is a Style embedding which turns everything in your image towards an Ancient Egyptian style! Think Pyramids, the river Nile, and Pharaohs! Simply throw Style-Hamunaptra_SD2 on to the end of your prompt (or the start, if the effect doesn't come through strong enough), and bam! - your picture is now Ancient Egypt-ified - it's as easy as that.

+10 internet points for getting the name reference.

This is an SD2.x version of my SD 1.5 Hamunaptra Style.

You can combine this embedding with other embeddings!

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
